  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dog is attracted by the bones and runs into a maze! You have to go in to find it and collect the bones on the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, this maze is not as simple as it seems. You may suddenly get into a whole new dimension.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362790/extras/8a0d04cd194a23ea9b45ccd407d931fe.poster.avif?t=1742109665\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362790/extras/8a0d04cd194a23ea9b45ccd407d931fe.webm?t=1742109665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362790/extras/8a0d04cd194a23ea9b45ccd407d931fe.mp4?t=1742109665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dog would like to jump, run and play with you! Find it quickly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362790/extras/7463379e86bb0df0d77bbb2d46d50f9e.poster.avif?t=1742109665\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362790/extras/7463379e86bb0df0d77bbb2d46d50f9e.webm?t=1742109665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362790/extras/7463379e86bb0df0d77bbb2d46d50f9e.mp4?t=1742109665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful hand-painted art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ordinary but brainwashing music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weird puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About 2 hours play time (But if you like, you can pass and collect all in 30 minutes!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space, dimension, the theme that interests you most!</p></li></ul>",
